description: Featuring the finest in authentic Belgian flavor, Tolmacsi Waffle is bringing you the best of everyone's favorite sweet breakfast treat! Featuring the amazing Marcel's genuine Belgian waffles, this food truck is serving up just what you're looking for in fantastic food. Made to order and topped with just what you want, every time you try a Tolmacsi Waffle is sure to be better than the last!
name: Tolmacsi Waffle
